<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

        integrity="sha384-NHtbx1Hf6ctHNdZmU28YfhGjB63gcU1YU64ttM+c0RxMKNBj67j+N/axpqTfdffo"

<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/pdfobject/2.1.1/pdfobject.js"
        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')

            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)

           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||

        integrity="sha384-NHtbx1Hf6ctHNdZmU28YfhGjB63gcU1YU64ttM+c0RxMKNBj67j+N/axpqTfdffo"

        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)

           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");

        integrity="sha384-NHtbx1Hf6ctHNdZmU28YfhGjB63gcU1YU64ttM+c0RxMKNBj67j+N/axpqTfdffo"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script src="/static/scripts/jquery/jquery.placeholder.js"></script>

<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/pdfobject/2.1.1/pdfobject.js"
        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

<script src="/static/scripts/jquery-ui/js/jquery-ui-1.9.2.custom.js"></script>

<script src="https://cdn.datatables.net/1.10.15/js/jquery.dataTables.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-NHtbx1Hf6ctHNdZmU28YfhGjB63gcU1YU64ttM+c0RxMKNBj67j+N/axpqTfdffo"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script src="/static/scripts/popper.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

<script src="/static/scripts/jquery/jquery.placeholder.js"></script>

<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/pdfobject/2.1.1/pdfobject.js"
        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

<script src="/static/scripts/jquery-ui/js/jquery-ui-1.9.2.custom.js"></script>

<script src="https://cdn.datatables.net/1.10.15/js/jquery.dataTables.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-NHtbx1Hf6ctHNdZmU28YfhGjB63gcU1YU64ttM+c0RxMKNBj67j+N/axpqTfdffo"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script src="/static/scripts/popper.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

<script src="/static/scripts/jquery/jquery.placeholder.js"></script>
<script src="/static/scripts/jquery/jquery.dPassword.js"></script>

<script src="/static/scripts/jquery/jquery.cooke.js"></script>

<!-- PDF -->
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/pdfobject/2.1.1/pdfobject.js"
        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<!-- PDF -->
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/pdfobject/2.1.1/pdfobject.js"
        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/pdfobject/2.1.1/pdfobject.js"
        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/pdfobject/2.1.1/pdfobject.js"
        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

<script src="/static/browser-detect.js"></script>

<!-- PDF -->
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/pdfobject/2.1.1/pdfobject.js"
        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/pdfobject/2.1.1/pdfobject.js"
        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

        integrity="sha384-NHtbx1Hf6ctHNdZmU28YfhGjB63gcU1YU64ttM+c0RxMKNBj67j+N/axpqTfdffo"

<!-- PDF -->
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/pdfobject/2.1.1/pdfobject.js"
        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {

        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/pdfobject/2.1.1/pdfobject.js"
        integrity="sha512-X6sgTijRHjRCltheFlgnf5Lm4NzCXVgfSNAHjHq4G8R03SBUTUVqFllStaiZflC4mEOtaPGRSWvcd3zFSl7eYg==" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
    {
        if (BrowserDetect.browser == "Explorer" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 11 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 36 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Safari" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 7 ||
            BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && parseInt(BrowserDetect.version, 10) < 31)
        {
           window.location.replace("/incompatible-browser/");
        }
    }
</script>

    $(document).ready( function(){

                    input.val('');

                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);

                        input.val('');

        }

            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;

            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    $(document).ready( function(){
        if(!Modernizr.input.placeholder){
            $('[placeholder]').focus(function() {
                var input = $(this);
                if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                    input.val('');
                    input.removeClass('placeholder');
                }
            }).blur(function() {
                        var input = $(this);
                        if (input.val() == '' || input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                            input.addClass('placeholder');
                            input.val(input.attr('placeholder'));
                        }
                    }).blur();
            $('[placeholder]').parents('form').submit(function() {
                $(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
                    var input = $(this);
                    if (input.val() == input.attr('placeholder')) {
                        input.val('');
                    }
                })
            });
        }


        //Popovers

        //Initializes popovers and provides target containers
        var i = 0;
        $(document).find('[data-toggle="popover"]').each(function(){;
            var popoverCount = 'popover'+i;
            i++;
            $(this).parent().addClass(popoverCount);
            var popoverContainer = '.' + popoverCount;
            $(this).popover({ container: popoverContainer});
          });

        //Hides popover if you click/touch away from it
        $(document).on('click touchstart', function (e) {
            $('[data-toggle="popover"],[data-original-title]').each(function () {
                if (!$(this).is(e.target) && $(this).has(e.target).length === 0 && $('.popover').has(e.target).length === 0) {
                    (($(this).popover('hide').data('bs.popover')||{}).inState||{}).click = false;
                }
            });
        });

        //Hides popover if press Esc
        $(document).keydown(function (e) {
            if (e.which === 27 && $(this).has('.popover')) {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            }
        });

        //Hides popover if you press close
        $(document).click(function() {
            $('button.close').click(function() {
                $('.popover').popover('hide');
            });
        });
    });


</script>

<script>
    if (window.location.pathname != '/incompatible-browser/')
